<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>大连市内慢性病检诊医院安排</strong></span></p>
<p>
<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><span style="text-align: center;"><strong><span>病 种</span></strong></span></td>
<td><span style="text-align: center;"><strong><span>检诊医院</span></strong></span></td>
</tr>
